{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce requirements for ethnic diversity in the workplace",
        "additional_details": "We want the Government to introduce new requirements for workplaces have proportional representation of ethnic minorities at all levels.\r\n \r\nWe need the Government to mandate that employers have a proportional representation of ethnic minorities at all levels of their organizations.\r\n \r\nCurrently, too many people from ethnic minorities are overlooked for promotions. Sometimes even having a non-British name can mean people do not get a job interview.\r\n \r\nTo fully develop as a nation, we must ensure equal opportunities for ethnic minorities, allowing them to access jobs at all levels.\r\n",
        "background": "People from ethnic minorities contribute significantly to the workforce and pay taxes, but they can be overlooked for promotion, especially to senior roles.",
